---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import SectionHeader from "./SectionHeader.astro";
import construction from "@images/under-construction.jpg";
---

<section aria-label="Services" id="services">
  <div class="description">
    <div>
      <SectionHeader
        ariaLabel="Services"
        color="white"
        href="#services"
        title="Services"
      />
      <p>
        As a full stack producer I focus on <mark
          >recording, mixing and editing</mark
        > your music. In addition, I offer other services to improve the quality
        of the recordings and prepare them for release on different media. For
        example
        <mark>streaming platforms, CD and vinyl</mark>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article aria-label="Recording" class="right" id="recording">
    <div class="text">
      <h3>
        Recording
        <a aria-label="Link to Recording" href="#recording">
          <span aria-hidden="true">üéôÔ∏è</span></a
        >
      </h3>
      <p>
        In the world of audio recording, it's all about you and your vision. I
        offer my services as an experienced recording engineer, available to be
        booked for external recording studios.
        <br aria-hidden="true" /><br aria-hidden="true" />
         My goal is simple: to help you
        <mark>capture the sound you envision for your final record</mark>. I
        understand the importance of your creative input, and I'm here to ensure
        your music comes to life just the way you want it.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <Image
        alt="Under construction sign"
        src={construction}
        height={construction.height}
        width={construction.width}
      />
    </div>
  </article>

  <hr aria-hidden="true" />

  <article aria-label="Editing" class="left" id="editing">
    <div class="image">
      <Image
        alt="Under construction sign"
        src={construction}
        height={construction.height}
        width={construction.width}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="text">
      <h3>
        Editing
        <a aria-label="Link to Editing" href="#editing">
          <span aria-hidden="true">‚úÇÔ∏è</span>
        </a>
      </h3>
      <br aria-hidden="true" />
      <p>
        When it comes to editing, I've spent plenty of time refining my skills,
        especially when it comes to <mark
          >instruments like drums, guitars, and bass</mark
        >. For vocals, I take the time to tune them with care.
        <br aria-hidden="true" /><br aria-hidden="true" />
         These behind-the-scenes processes are essential to achieving a polished
        and professional sound. My role is to make your music sound its best,
        one note at a time, setting the stage for a spectacular final mix.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <hr aria-hidden="true" />

  <article aria-label="Mixing" class="right" id="mixing">
    <div class="text">
      <h3>
        Mixing
        <a aria-label="Link to Mixing" href="#mixing">
          <span aria-hidden="true">üéöÔ∏è</span>
        </a>
      </h3>
      <br aria-hidden="true" />
      <p>
        With a focus on <mark>genres like Rock, Metal, Pop, and Rap</mark>, I've
        had the privilege of working with diverse musical styles. My aim is
        simple: to provide you with a competitive and compelling mix.
        <br aria-hidden="true" /><br aria-hidden="true" />
         I'll take your project and elevate it to new heights, ensuring it meets
        industry standards. Let's work together to make your music shine in its
        own unique way, without losing sight of your artistic essence.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <Image
        alt="Under construction sign"
        src={construction}
        height={construction.height}
        width={construction.width}
      />
    </div>
  </article>

  <hr aria-hidden="true" />

  <article aria-label="Mastering" class="left" id="mastering">
    <div class="image">
      <Image
        alt="Under construction sign"
        src={construction}
        height={construction.height}
        width={construction.width}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="text">
      <h3>
        Mastering
        <a aria-label="Link to Mastering" href="#mastering">
          <span aria-hidden="true">‚ú®</span>
        </a>
      </h3>
      <br aria-hidden="true" />
      <p>
        I work to enhance the overall clarity, depth, and impact of your
        content, making it shine with professional quality.
        <br aria-hidden="true" /><br aria-hidden="true" />
         With a keen ear and a commitment to preserving the integrity of your
        sound, <mark
          >I'm here to deliver audio that stands the test of time</mark
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <hr aria-hidden="true" />

  <article aria-label="Restoration" class="right" id="restoration">
    <div class="text">
      <h3>
        Restoration
        <a aria-label="Link to Restoration" href="#restoration">
          <span aria-hidden="true">üîß</span>
        </a>
      </h3>
      <br aria-hidden="true" />
      <p>
        If your audio has seen better days, my restoration expertise can <mark
          >breathe new life into old or damaged recordings</mark
        >, salvaging precious moments from the past.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image">
      <Image
        alt="Under construction sign"
        src={construction}
        height={construction.height}
        width={construction.width}
      />
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  section {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  a {
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .description {
    background: black;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl) auto;

    div {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 768px;
      padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-xs);
    }

    p {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }

  article {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1536px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-xs);
    scroll-margin-top: var(--space-3xl);

    .image {
      align-self: center;

      img {
        max-height: 450px;
        object-fit: cover;
        width: auto;
      }
    }

    .text {
      align-items: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 70ch;
    }

    h3 {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    }
  }

  [aria-label="Recording"] {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
